WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.130 --> 00:00:10.800
Sadhguru: Yoga for Joy – Nada yoga.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:18.370
Modern science is proving to you the whole
existence is just a reverberation.

00:00:18.370 --> 00:00:22.090
Where there is a reverberation, there is bound
to be a sound.

00:00:22.090 --> 00:00:28.860
So, the whole existence is sound.

00:00:28.860 --> 00:00:39.110
The root sounds for this complex amalgamation
of sounds are aaa, ooo and mmm.

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:45.360
Without employing your tongue, you would be
able to make only these three sounds –

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:47.520
aaa, ooo and mmma.

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:51.760
By placing your tongue in different positions
within the cavity of your mouth,

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:56.720
you get to mix these three sounds and produce all the
other sounds.

00:00:56.760 --> 00:01:03.079
Aaa, ooo and mmm are the basis of all the
other sounds that you can utter.

00:01:03.079 --> 00:01:08.180
They are referred to as the basic sounds or
the universal sounds.

00:01:08.180 --> 00:01:15.039
If you utter these three sounds together,
you get the sound AUM.

00:01:15.039 --> 00:01:19.310
These are the only three sounds that the system
can produce naturally.

00:01:19.310 --> 00:01:21.547
If you utter these three sounds carefully,

00:01:21.547 --> 00:01:26.240
different aspects of your body are activated and energized.

00:01:26.240 --> 00:01:32.240
You will notice if you utter the sound aaa,
the reverberation starts just beneath the navel and

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:37.440
will spread right across the
body because this is the only place where

00:01:37.499 --> 00:01:45.079
all the 72,000 nadis or pathways of energy
meet and redistribute themselves.

00:01:45.079 --> 00:01:51.159
This is the maintenance center in the body,
uttering the sound aaa strengthens this.

00:01:51.159 --> 00:01:57.440
If you utter the sound ooo, you will notice
this point where the ribcage meets,

00:01:57.440 --> 00:02:00.000
just beneath that, there is a soft spot.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:05.040
The reverberations will flow from here and then move upward

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:06.880
If you utter the sound mmm,

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:10.240
you will see the reverberations will start from the pit of your throat,

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:14.160
and generally spread to the uppper regions of your body.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:17.440
Uttering these sounds has innumerable benefits.

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:23.760
If you are suffering from any psychological
disturbances like excessive fear, nightmares,

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:27.030
or unstable mind or body,

00:02:27.040 --> 00:02:31.760
if your general constitution is weak, you
tend to fall sick too often,

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:34.880
particularly for children who have attention disorders,

00:02:34.880 --> 00:02:38.720
daily utterance of these sounds for a few minutes a day

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:40.710
will make an enormous difference.

00:02:40.710 --> 00:02:47.980
Uttering of these three fundamental sounds
activates the three lobes of your lungs separately,

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:52.080
which in turn activates the three basic segments
of the body –

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:54.815
the lower, the middle, and the upper –

00:02:54.815 --> 00:02:59.360
laying the necessary foundation
for the pleasantness of your being

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:04.000
or for a joyful existence.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:08.960
Here are a few guidelines that will set optimal
conditions and

00:03:08.960 --> 00:03:12.240
greatly enhance your receptivity of the practices.

00:03:12.880 --> 00:03:17.920
Please ensure cell phones are either in silent
mode or switched off.

00:03:17.920 --> 00:03:22.000
It is advisable not to sit for the program
with a full stomach

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:24.720
or immediately after a meal.

00:03:24.720 --> 00:03:31.040
Please sit with your spine comfortably erect,
hands uncrossed and palms open.

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:36.560
These conditions will prepare you to be in
a heightened state of receptivity and

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:39.600
derive the most benefits from the practices.

00:03:39.600 --> 00:03:45.840
These practices are very safe and simple and
can be done by anybody.

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:54.080
The practices we will be learning here can
be done by anyone ages 7 years and above.

00:03:54.080 --> 00:04:01.840
If you wear glasses, while doing the yoga
practices, please remove them and keep them aside.

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:04.880
Sit in a cross-legged posture.

00:04:04.930 --> 00:04:09.650
Place your palms facing upward upon your thighs.

00:04:09.650 --> 00:04:14.650
Listen to the instructions carefully before
you start the practice.

00:04:14.650 --> 00:04:34.000
Open your mouth wide enough and utter the
sound aaa (Sadhguru demonstrates a full ‘aaa’)

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:36.060
- completely exhaling into the sound.

00:04:36.060 --> 00:04:38.340
We’ll do this seven times.

00:04:38.340 --> 00:04:42.880
Then, shape your lips in the form of a circle and

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:58.480
utter the sound ooo (Sadhguru demonstrates a full ‘ooo’)

00:04:58.480 --> 00:05:01.840
- completely exhaling into the sound.

00:05:01.840 --> 00:05:03.680
We’ll do this seven times.

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:06.000
Then, by closing your mouth,

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:25.360
utter the sound mmm (Sadhguru demonstrates a full ‘mmm’).

00:05:25.370 --> 00:05:28.790
You utter the sound mmm seven times.

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:34.560
As you do this, notice where the reverberations
are happening, in which region of the body.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:39.200
Sound aaa generates reverberations around your navel,

00:05:39.200 --> 00:05:42.880
sound ooo at the point where the ribcage meets,

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:47.760
and sound mmm will center around
the pit of your throat.

00:05:47.780 --> 00:05:49.870
Now, let us do it together.

00:05:49.870 --> 00:05:54.980
Keep your palms facing upward, your spine
comfortably erect.

00:05:54.980 --> 00:05:59.280
Please close your eyes.

00:05:59.280 --> 00:07:57.840
(Sadhguru demonstrates a full aaa seven times)

00:07:57.840 --> 00:09:54.320
(Sadhguru demonstrates a full ooo seven times)

00:09:54.320 --> 00:11:59.040
(Sadhguru demonstrates a full mmm seven times)

00:11:59.040 --> 00:12:08.400
Take your own time, take your own time, slowly,
very slowly, open your eyes.

00:12:08.400 --> 00:12:11.000
[Explore 5 minuts for Joy] Joy is not a rare happening.

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:14.000
It is not an achievement or an attainment.

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:17.440
It should be the natural ambience of your life.

00:12:17.440 --> 00:12:22.720
When you remain joyful, your whole life is a celebration.

